_:Ne240dc22410f45a2b088f2453a1c08d3 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Andrew Western was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Department of Work and Pensions on 9 July 2024. He was elected as the MP for Stretford and Urmston in July 2024.</p>\n" .
